      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 608,
      "message": "It is better to rely on the URL object instead of a raw String to represent the endpoint, since a String type is too generic by itself.\nI have made a different simplification by getting rid of the UriBuilder and just relying on simple new URL() from java.net. There is no need to have a builder since it is not even fully utilized.",
